name: Shakedown Boulevard "Heart Of A Fighter" CD
description:
Heart Of A Fighter is the debut album from West Virginia "High Energy American Rock & Roll" band, Shakedown Boulevard.  Featuring 14 tracks of passionate punk rock and roll music.  Produced by Bud Carroll and recorded at Smash Hits Studios (Huntington, WV) by Steve Riley from November 2010 - April 2011.

For fans of Tom Petty & the Heartbreakers, Bruce Springsteen & the E Street Band, The Gaslight Anthem and The Rolling Stones. 

Released independently on October 4, 2011.

Shipping is FREE and your order will come with buttons and stickers.
